title: Hermes Birkin 30 Handbag
description: Hermes Birkin 30 in Blue Taurillon Clemence leather (Square I: 2005). Featuring silver-toned hardware, rolled top handles, frontal flap with closure straps & turn-lock mechanism. The top flap opens to a colour matching leather interior with patch and zipper pocket. Approx. dimensions: 30cm(L) x 22cm(H) x 16cm(D), handle drop 10cm. Accompanied by Hermes twilly scarf, keys in leather clochette, padlock and dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
